{"tid":1486144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 有證據顯示發覺多左好多和理非左膠上連登","createTime":"2019-08-18T18:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T19:46:55.000Z","uid":167548,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbbee9599cea96087853968cf0a0546e030873b","tid":1486144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:53:42.000Z","msg":"如果個位巴打見到請體證, 但是有必要提<span style=\"color: red;\">連登核心價值</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源開左個Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">突發 有鑒於連登開始對前線有怨言指責 請入一入嚟贊下班即走有勇有謀勇武。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dGviPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dGviPS</a></span><br />\n<br />\n覆左下手足, 竟然有禮貌回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBBEwEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBBEwEv.jpg&h=17068058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起一起底 #283xxx <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提左膠和理非勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋甩左P唔好見P牌就屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是呢個Post重點都是下面呢幅題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lq7kf7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLq7kf7e.png&h=39ebc61f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c8c8d43599694cebd4fee1956ca5aeceb09a2b1","tid":1486144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:54:20.000Z","msg":"想問問是味我太sensitive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f3faf57f973e95452dbdfc1fecc91afc9a36df","tid":1486144,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"［永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進］今日總結，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485890</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成（搶佔國際輿論），冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得可能唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同一時間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己做最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，加上客觀因素（現場人多電話收到嘅信號會少/ 局勢變化可能太快）散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度，兵荒馬亂之際大家嘅心情難免心急，語氣上亦會有所失儀，唯希望大家之後仍然可以再度團結，齊上齊落，打贏呢一場逆權運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89ccdb7508ad19bad1146b95c34f5419ac291bb","tid":1486144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"第一次見有連登甘樣回<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6062e148bc2c5d316ccd017fe089aed88a554d3","tid":1486144,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:55:08.000Z","msg":"借推<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇留意，今日8點幾9點嘅時候，夏愨道D車係一堆咁連續駛入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae85606c4bb5954466d1ab4ed3af70daf4693f16","tid":1486144,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好咁啦"},{"pid":"c634853103608e9d956acb0aac8f6b4d2ea559dd","tid":1486144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae85606c4bb5954466d1ab4ed3af70daf4693f16","tid":1486144,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好咁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:55:40.000Z","msg":"要鞭一鞭佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73514d05f2ad740264659dda5350c2d747e0b06","tid":1486144,"uid":285523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"唔想見連登返去「港女都係家禽」、「00/10後都係垃圾」、「廢中/老」、「蝻/蛔」個分化mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上有唔少今次都積極參與，咁樣批評都幾唔厚道"},{"pid":"5c83e1214b39e6349e5f422ccdb49661b46c2458","tid":1486144,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:01:52.000Z","msg":"再睇連登班左膠真係會爆血管"},{"pid":"0ec1192123bc5979745ab93230be1bcac3178545","tid":1486144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73514d05f2ad740264659dda5350c2d747e0b06","tid":1486144,"uid":285523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"唔想見連登返去「港女都係家禽」、「00/10後都係垃圾」、「廢中/老」、「蝻/蛔」個分化mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上有唔少今次都積極參與，咁樣批評都幾唔厚道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:03:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗驚唔會番到去, We Connected <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2102e47a9c71dff5ec44a09cb65f23b2db37f718","tid":1486144,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"返5p啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86f01f0ac464ae690015c454546c3c88bc4128f","tid":1486144,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f89ccdb7508ad19bad1146b95c34f5419ac291bb","tid":1486144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"repl